## Avoid These Anti-patterns

```tsx
// ❌ Don't use arbitrary values when Tailwind provides them
<div className="p-[16px]">  // Bad - use p-4

// ❌ Don't mix Tailwind with inline styles
<div className="flex" style={{ gap: '8px' }}>  // Bad - use gap-2

// ❌ Don't create unnecessary CSS files
// Most styling should be done with Tailwind utilities

// ❌ Don't use light themes in DevTools context
<div className="bg-white text-black">  // Bad for DevTools
```
